<br>
Grab a cleric level 44-46 with you.<br>
Summon an earth elemental pet and buff him, DS him.<br>
Pull the hunter with best malosini.<br>
Send pet and wait for the pet's life equal 80 %.<br>
Nuke both time with scirroco or manastorm.<br>
Cleric cast CH when pet's life equal 40% (2-3 time during fight).<br>
Hunter dead.<br>
<br>
3 minutes fight = 1% exp at level 59 (for me)= 1%exp at level 44-46 (for the cleric).<br>
<br>
Rinse and repeat<br>
<br>
<br>
----------------------------------------------------<br>
<br>
Another good idea<br>
<br>
Grab your best friend (Master Wiz 60) and a cleric level 44-46.<br>
Go to Maiden Eye at safe spot near the Xi spire.<br>
WIz hard quad (pull 10-16 mobs - Toilers, wolf, skel, Wurm, Bat).<br>
WIz take all the mob down.<br>
You take the exp seeing an undimensionnal fight<br>
You rod him<br>
Cleric heal him.<br>
<br>
Rinse and repeat.<br>
<br>
Every hard quad = 1/2 BB - 3/4 BB regular exp at level 59 = 20 min fight.<br>
<br>
Never seen my exp bar moving so fast since level 49.<br>
